Functions.
  R A.
  R B.
  R S.
  R a().
End.

ProgramVariables.
  R x.
  R v.
  R a.
End.

Problem.
    v >= 0 & A > 0 & B > 0 & x+v^2/(2*B) < S
 -> [
      { {   ?x+v^2/(2*B) < S; a := A
         ++ ?v=0; a := 0
         ++ a := -B
        };
        ?a()=a; /* needed because we neither support a() := nor v'=a */

        {x' = v, v' = a() & v >= 0 & x+v^2/(2*B) <= S ++ x' = v, v' = a() & v >= 0 & x+v^2/(2*B) >= S}
      }*@invariant(v >= 0 & x+v^2/(2*B) <= S)
    ] x <= S
End.